《這個美妙的世界》获得积极评价与商业成功。《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》授予其2008年5月月度掌机游戏奖。[[IGN|IGN]]授予游戏编辑推荐奖，并将其列为4月月度DS游戏<ref name="ign gotm">{{cite web | url = http://ds.ign.com/articles/870/870825p1.html | title = IGN: Game of the Month: April 2008 | first = Daemon | last = Hatfield | publisher = IGN | date = 2008-04-30 | accessdate = 2008-06-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.li/20110607015556/http://ds.ign.com/articles/870/870825p1.html | archivedate = 2011-06-07 }}</ref>。游戏在日本首发周成为该统计周第二畅销DS游戏<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=14847 | title = Saling The World: Guitar Hero Encore Tops Charts in U.S. and UK | date = 2007-07-27 | accessdate = 2008-06-18 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | first = Danny | last = Cowan | archive-date = 2012-10-03 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6B8D183y8?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=14847 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。游戏2007年在日本售出19.3万套<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.n4g.com/industrynews/News-157766.aspx | title = Japanese 2007 Top 500 Game Sales (by Famitsu) | publisher = News 4 Gamers | date = 2008-06-13 | accessdate = 2008-07-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080618095552/http://www.n4g.com/industrynews/News-157766.aspx | archivedate = 2008-06-18 }}</ref>。《這個美妙的世界》2008年4月间在北美售出4.3万套<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/newsArt.cfm?artid=16022 | title = April NPD: Nintendo Unfazed By Competition | publisher = {{tsl|en|Nintendo World|}} Report | first = Carmine | last = Red | date = 2008-05-27 | accessdate = 2008-06-18 | archive-date = 2012-10-03 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6B8D2MtSr?url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/16022 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。第一批出货于5月中旬售罄<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/column_index.php?story=8854 | title = Saling The World: GTA IV, Mario Kart Lead US, Luminous Arc 2 Tops Japan | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2008-05-15 | accessdate = 2008-06-18 | first = Danny | last = Cowan | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080521170338/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/column_index.php?story=8854 | archivedate = 2008-05-21 }}</ref>，第二批出货于2008年6月中旬发出<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.joystiq.com/2008/06/03/the-world-ends-with-you-new-shipment-coming-mid-june/ | title = The World Ends With You: new shipment coming mid-June | publisher = Joystiq | first = Ross | last = Miller | date = 2008-06-03 | accessdate = 2008-06-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150128063517/http://www.joystiq.com/2008/06/03/the-world-ends-with-you-new-shipment-coming-mid-june/ | archivedate = 2015-01-28 }}</ref>。游戏发行首周成为最畅销DS游戏<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/column_index.php?story=8845 | title = Saling The World: The World Ends With You, Persona 3 FES Top Sales in U.S. Debut Week | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2008-04-24 | accessdate = 2008-06-18 | first = Danny | last = Cowan | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080428230016/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/column_index.php?story=8845 | archivedate = 2008-04-28 }}</ref>，并于两周后再度登顶<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/column_index.php?story=8851 | title = Saling The World: GTAIV Repeats U.S. and UK Sales Victory | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2008-05-08 | accessdate = 2008-06-18 | first = Danny | last = Cowan | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080611065202/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/column_index.php?story=8851 | archivedate = 2008-06-11 }}</ref>。截至2008年9月30日，《這個美妙的世界》在北美售出约14万套，在欧洲售出约2万套<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/5081606/which-square-enix-games-have-been-selling-this-year | title = Which Square Enix Games Have Been Selling This Year | publisher = Kotaku | date = 2008-11-10 | accessdate = 2008-11-10 | first = Brian | last = Ashcraft | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6B8D46x5R?url=http://kotaku.com/5081606/which-square-enix-games-have-been-selling-this-year | archive-date = 2012-10-03 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

评论称赞游戏与史克威尔艾尼克斯的[[最终幻想|最终幻想]]与[[王国之心|王国之心]]等畅销游戏有着巨大不同<ref name="ign review" /><ref name="ign gotm" />。图形呈现和原声都获得高度评价<ref name="ign review" /><ref name="eurogamer review" /><ref name="gamespot review">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamespot.com/ds/rpg/wonderfulworld/review.html?page=2 | title = The World Ends With You for DS Review | publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | first = Randolph | last = Ramsay | date = 2008-04-22 | accessdate = 2008-06-19 | archive-date = 2008-12-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081201115901/http://www.gamespot.com/ds/rpg/wonderfulworld/review.html?page=2 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。评论还认为，最初，角色设计和之前的史克威尔艾尼克斯作品太过相似，且从某种角度令人扫兴<ref name="1up review" /><ref name="gamespot review" />，尽管使用涩谷设定中的他们“绝对有着他们的元素”<ref name="1up review" />。一些评论还因跨越战斗系统对新玩家太过复杂而不满<ref name="1up review">{{cite web | url = http://www.1up.com/do/reviewPage?cId=3167457&p=39&sec=REVIEWS | title = Reviews: The World Ends With You | publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | first = Jeremy | last = Parish | date = 2008-04-17 | accessdate = 2008-06-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6B8D4mPKF?url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/world-ends | archivedate = 2012-10-03 }}</ref>；[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的评论认为“全靠自己”来学习复杂的战斗系统是游戏的重大障碍<ref name="eurogamer review" />。《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》认为[[触屏笔|触屏笔]]输入不够精准，经常误移动或发动攻击<ref name="gamepro review">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamepro.com/nintendo/ds/games/reviews/178928.shtml | title = Review: The World Ends With You | date = 2008-04-22 | accessdate = 2008-06-19 | first = Amanda | last = Ng | work = [[GamePro|GamePro]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080424080309/http://www.gamepro.com/nintendo/ds/games/reviews/178928.shtml | archivedate = 2008-04-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。另一方面，系统因其很亲和，可以改变游戏系统难度而获得赞扬<ref name="1up review" /><ref name="gamespot review" />。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的评论总结称，游戏远超其各部分的总和：“不管怎样来说，《這個美妙的世界》都应是一噱头、老生常谈。但不知何故，所有本应难以忍受的东西都开始有条不紊，并创造了一款比本来远为独特、有趣、令人上瘾的游戏。”<ref name="1up review" />

《這個美妙的世界》获得[[IGN|IGN]]网站的数项奖项，包括最佳任天堂DS角色扮演游戏<ref name="ignrpg">{{cite web |title=IGN DS: Best RPG 2008 |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/7.html |publisher=IGN.com |accessdate=2008-12-16 |date=2008-12-15 |archive-date=2011-08-14 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60vDFU9n4?url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/7.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、任天堂DS游戏最佳剧情<ref name="ignstory">{{cite web |title=IGN DS: Best Story 2008 |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/16.html |publisher=IGN.com |accessdate=2008-12-16 |date=2008-12-15 |archive-date=2008-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219041943/http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/16.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、最佳DS新[[知识产权|知识产权]]<ref name="ignip">{{cite web |title=IGN DS: Best New IP 2008 |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/19.html |publisher=IGN.com |accessdate=2008-12-16 |date=2008-12-15 |archive-date=2008-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219041958/http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/19.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及最佳年度任天堂DS游戏<ref name="igngoty">{{cite web |title=IGN DS: DS Game of the Year 2008 |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/21.html |publisher=IGN.com |accessdate=2008-12-15 |date=2008-12-15 |archive-date=2008-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219041351/http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/21.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏还获得其它奖项提名，包括任天堂DS游戏最佳原声配乐<ref name="ignscore">{{cite web |title=IGN DS: Best Original Score 2008 |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/14.html |publisher=IGN.com |accessdate=2008-12-16 |date=2008-12-15 |archive-date=2013-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101162335/http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/14.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及最佳任天堂DS游戏艺术设计<ref name="igndesign">{{cite web |title=IGN DS: Best Artistic Design 2008 |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/13.html |publisher=IGN.com |accessdate=2008-12-16 |date=2008-12-15 |archive-date=2008-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219041933/http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/13.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏获得《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》最佳2000年代任天堂系统游戏第十名<ref>{{cite journal |title=The Best of the Decade |journal=Nintendo Power |issue=252 |date=March 2010 }}</ref>。

《這個美妙的世界 -独奏混音-》获得IGN的9.5分与编辑推荐奖，他们称赞了游戏移植与追加要素，但对零售价和通用兼容性（iPhone/iPad Touch和iPad版游戏必须分别购买）表示批评<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2012/08/27/the-world-ends-with-you-solo-remix-review |title=The World Ends with You: Solo Remix Review - IGN |publisher=Uk.ign.com |date=2012-08-27 |accessdate=2012-11-07 |archive-date=2012-10-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B9K9svEB?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/08/27/the-world-ends-with-you-solo-remix-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]也批评游戏的高价与无通用兼容性“站不住脚”，但他们也称赞了游戏在操作性上的移植“在许多方面，（iPad版）比其DS版的感觉更舒适”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5938263/the-world-ends-with-you-is-actually-a-pretty-good-port |title=The World Ends With You Is Actually A Pretty Good Port |publisher=Kotaku.com |date=2012-08-27 |accessdate=2012-11-07 |archive-date=2012-10-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B9KAcTDr?url=http://kotaku.com/5938263/the-world-ends-with-you-is-actually-a-pretty-good-port |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

